      "writtenOn": "2019-01-22T19:56:10Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I recommend using the video injection proto directly here instead of serializing to a string.  The reason that automation was serialized to a string is that I intended the data to be opaque-- the only source that creates it is the emulator EventGenerated callback, and then it should be replayed as-is through the replay API.\n\nFor this, we need to craft commands in the client library, so having a layer of indirection doesn\u0027t help.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 119,
        "startChar": 2,
        "endLine": 121,
        "endChar": 3
      },
      "revId": "492cd26de5263d86145dc58bce9cd4b899f11974",
      "serverId": "85c56323-6fa9-3386-8a01-6480fb634889",
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
