      "side": 1,
      "message": "Having video playback within the Automation struct seems a bit ambiguous, since there are things like \"replay\" that don\u0027t pertain to video.  Consider hoisting this out to the same level as Snapshot/Automation, creating a VideoInjectionRequest/Response and adding it to the Request/Response module oneof instead.",
